{"tid":2382974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貴州女子微信群罵社區支書「草包支書」被警方跨市拘留","createTime":"2021-01-27T15:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T03:26:56.000Z","uid":13503,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0080480f1582a7001bcd62fcd28b62cec8efc352","tid":2382974,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>因為微信群里罵了一句「草包支書」，貴州省貴陽市的任女士被跨市銬走並行拘3日。1月27日，任女士談及此事表示：「<span class=\"red\">當時的情況就是那些警察可以輕易決定他人的人身自由，異地傳喚的程序一直到他們區公安局的層面都沒發現問題，給我下達拘留通知的時候，我要求聯繫律師，那邊警察說我港片看多了&hellip;&hellip;</span>」<br />\n<br />\n任女士證實，1月26日以來，採訪她的記者很多。「這個事情本來不想讓媒體曝光，但是通過12389（注：全國公安機關和民警違紀違法舉報電話）舉報2個多月了一直沒有回復&hellip;&hellip;他們所有的證據就那一句話。」<br />\n<br />\n1月26日晚，畢節市公安局發佈警情通報稱，撤銷對任女士的行政處罰，涉案的派出所所長和民警已停職接受調查。任女士承認，她看到畢節警方的通報，她用「回到陽間了！」來形容</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBOC3jH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBOC3jH.png&h=ebf681e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eg3rWEJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEg3rWEJ.png&h=2cd0f3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfMUk6o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfMUk6o.png&h=67d07587&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef94f5c1c98701026243900902e69eb95489cd02","tid":2382974,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"lamentable quisling figure呢？"},{"pid":"d7dd348f4e540f9d8f2d0e2599d4f716ade7c673","tid":2382974,"uid":123774,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"國民滿意度98%"},{"pid":"e520d8eecd0c5642d86ce41a29b170f8e364e2ce","tid":2382974,"uid":151074,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"其實支那要律師呢個職業做乜？記者都唔應該有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s